        "template--15521095417901__3654b6e8-4701-4939-8a8f-5514a6dee111-167916405687b3c1db-0": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What are the hours of operation?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Monday-Friday from 10am - 6pm EST</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15521095417901__3654b6e8-4701-4939-8a8f-5514a6dee111-167916405687b3c1db-1": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you ship to international customers?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Products on the website are currently available to US residents only. If you live outside of the United States, contact us to see if RSP is available in stores near you. You may also choose to order from our product page on iHerb.com.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15521095417901__3654b6e8-4701-4939-8a8f-5514a6dee111-167916405687b3c1db-2": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "I have a product I am unsure if it's legitimate, who do I contact?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>If you are questioning the authenticity of the product, please contact us. Along with your message, include the Lot Number (can be found underneath the product), Images of the product, and where the product was purchased (State/Country and Store Name).</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15521095417901__3654b6e8-4701-4939-8a8f-5514a6dee111-167916405687b3c1db-3": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I cancel my order I just placed?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Our team works very hard to ship your order as soon as possible. You may be eligible to cancel an order if it has not left our warehouse. Please contact us immediately with all necessary information such as order number, name and shipping address to assist.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "87b1f207-fae3-402f-91c6-cb999742d4e5": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I change the shipping address?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Please contact our support team in order to update your shipping address. Our team works very hard to ship your order as soon as possible, so it is important you contact us ASAP as we cannot make changes once your order has shipped.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "44960bad-4e2e-4226-96f7-49fa7595f7b1": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "I have forgotten my password, how can I get a new one?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>If you have forgotten your password, you can reset your password through our website. Simply go to <a href=\"http://www.rspnutrition.com/\" target=\"_blank\">www.rspnutrition.com </a>click on Log In then click on reset password and follow the steps. If for any reason you have trouble resetting your password, please do not hesitate to contact our support team.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "60fee00f-8e1b-4079-8591-38455f641239": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I change my password?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>You can reset/change your password through our website. Simply go to <a href=\"http://www.rspnutrition.com/\" target=\"_blank\">www.rspnutrition.com</a> click on Log In then click on reset password and follow the steps. If for any reason you have trouble resetting your password, please do not hesitate to contact our support team.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "bc9de9ef-209a-4c63-9fc4-db2499e1c64c": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I change the email address on my account?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Please contact our support team in order to have your email address changed for your account. Make sure to include the current email address associated with your account.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "967c0887-3a30-4d96-b570-e6f80ae2bf0b": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I create an account?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Accounts can be created two ways, when you order for the first time you will be asked if you would like to create an account while checking out. Or, if you prefer to register directly, simply go to <a href=\"http://www.rspnutrition.com/\" target=\"_blank\">www.rspnutrition.com</a> and click on sign up or click on the link below (United States customers).</p><p> <a href=\"https://rspnutrition.com/account/register\" target=\"_blank\">https://rspnutrition.com/account/register</a></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "7b6d4c3c-b97e-4391-894a-7d062186494f": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How to Track my order?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Once your order is processed you will receive an email confirmation with tracking information. You may also find tracking information by going to <a href=\"http://www.rspnutrition.com/\" target=\"_blank\">www.rspnutrition.com</a>, logging into your account and clicking on Orders. Once you click on the order in question you will find tracking information. If you have any trouble, please do not hesitate to contact our support team. </p><p>Orders placed before 12 pm Eastern Time usually ship within 1-2 business days. Any orders placed after 12pm Eastern Time will ship the following 1-2 business days. All orders are received within 4-5 business days of the ship date.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
