          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I return a product that I do not like?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes, if you do not like a product you may return it within 30 days of ordering for a full refund or a replacement product of your choice.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15521095417901__1a7ca64d-8ab5-4d7a-b946-9c0b18b9131c-167916405687b3c1db-1": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What do I do if a receive a product that is damaged or a product that has no seal?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes, if you receive a product that is damaged and/or has a torn or no seal you may return it within 30 days of ordering for a full refund or a replacement product of your choice</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15521095417901__1a7ca64d-8ab5-4d7a-b946-9c0b18b9131c-167916405687b3c1db-2": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where do I ship my return?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Returns should be addressed to: </p><p>RSP Nutrition <br/>3381 NW 168th Street <br/>Miami Gardens, FL 33056</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15521095417901__1a7ca64d-8ab5-4d7a-b946-9c0b18b9131c-167916405687b3c1db-3": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you have a money back guarantee?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes,we offer a 100% money back guaranteewithin 30 days if you are not happy with the product(s) or run into a manufacturer defect.  Just reach out to aCustomer Service Representative at <strong>(877) 814-2544,</strong> or email <a href=\"mailto:support@rspnutrition.com\">support@rspnutrition.com</a> for assistance.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
